issue.title: VISPAT(?) Assessment Form

milestone.title: Week One
milestone.description: First week of development, two weeks before the deadline.

issue.body: Lets use redux to collect the state of the assessment form, so that a user can input all of the data and keep it in the redux store. Very similar to the implementation for the dept-ag-form. Let's keep the form simple and modular enough so that we can consider making the questions extensible / editable via a CMS that will allow administrators to change the values dynamically.
